column5: I saw this today and thought i'd share.<iframe src="https://www.facebook.com/video/embed?video_id=10151613265769919" width="654" height="480" frameborder="0"></iframe>

You can never judge a book by its color, which ive been known to do myself, thanx for posting, my issue is governments both Canada and the US, will send millions to foreign countries, while our own sleep on the streets, not knowing where their next meal is coming from, and many of those are war veterans, who fought for our freedoms.
